FastPattern.matcher: (\d+) ([-\w.]+) \d \d+\.\d+ ([\w ]+) events dhcp lease of ip ([\d.]+) from server mac ([A-F\d:]+) for client mac ([A-F\d:]+) from router ([\d.]+) on subnet ([\d.]+)(.*)

FastPattern.matcher: (\d+) ([-\w.]+) \d \d+\.\d+ ([\w ]+) events DHCP: no free DHCP leases to give ([A-Fa-f\d:]+) on network ([\d.]+\/\d+).*
